[176.184938, "o", "\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[176.186251, "o", "3:Store notes in /app/data/notes.db. Read the shared secret from /app/config/api.key and trim surrounding whitespace before comparing it to the X-API-Key header on mutating requests. The stock api.key file ships with tb3_notes_api_secret_2026. POST, PUT, and DELETE require a matching key or the server responds unauthorized. GET never requires the key; a bad or missing key on a mutating call is unauthorized.\r\n"]
[176.186423, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@08d5c4164ec3:/app# "]
[176.304453, "i", "sed -n '1,220p' /app/src/routes.h /app/src/static.c /app/src/static.h\n"]
